│ 708 /// An extension of the inner loop vectorizer that creates a skeleton for a         │
│ 709 /// vectorized loop that has its epilogue (residual) also vectorized.               │
│ 710 /// The idea is to run the vplan on a given loop twice, firstly to setup the        │
│ 711 /// skeleton and vectorize the main loop, and secondly to complete the skeleton     │
│ 712 /// from the first step and vectorize the epilogue.  This is achieved by            │
│ 713 /// deriving two concrete strategy classes from this base class and invoking        │
│ 714 /// them in succession from the loop vectorizer planner.                            │
