│ 956 /// LoopVectorizationCostModel - estimates the expected speedups due to             │
│ 957 /// vectorization.                                                                  │
│ 958 /// In many cases vectorization is not profitable. This can happen because of       │
│ 959 /// a number of reasons. In this class we mainly attempt to predict the             │
